{
  "video_id": "FjvjSlpJoqo",
  "title": "The economic injustice of plastic | Van Jones",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 20236.0,
      "end_time": 21624.0,
      "text": "I am honored to be here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21648.0,
      "end_time": 23625.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m honored to talk about this topic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23649.0,
      "end_time": 25474.0,
      "text": "which I think is of grave importance."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25498.0,
      "end_time": 26721.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been talking a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26745.0,
      "end_time": 32688.0,
      "text": "about the horrific impacts of plastic on the planet and on other species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32712.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34720.0,
      "text": "but plastic hurts people, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35211.0,
      "end_time": 36593.0,
      "text": "especially poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 40418.0,
      "text": "And both in the production of plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40442.0,
      "end_time": 43160.0,
      "text": "the use of plastic and the disposal of plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43184.0,
      "end_time": 45748.0,
      "text": "the people who have the bull&#39;s-eye on their foreheads"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45773.0,
      "end_time": 47463.0,
      "text": "are poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47487.0,
      "end_time": 50564.0,
      "text": "People got very upset"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50588.0,
      "end_time": 53667.0,
      "text": "when the BP oil spill happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53691.0,
      "end_time": 55151.0,
      "text": "for very good reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55175.0,
      "end_time": 56799.0,
      "text": "People thought, \"Oh, my God."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56823.0,
      "end_time": 59599.0,
      "text": "This is terrible, this oil -- it&#39;s in the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59623.0,
      "end_time": 63541.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to destroy the living systems there."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63565.0,
      "end_time": 64998.0,
      "text": "People are going to be hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65220.0,
      "end_time": 66514.0,
      "text": "This is a terrible thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66538.0,
      "end_time": 68872.0,
      "text": "this oil is going to hurt the people in the Gulf.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68897.0,
      "end_time": 70967.0,
      "text": "What people don&#39;t think about is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70991.0,
      "end_time": 73150.0,
      "text": "What if the oil had made it safely to shore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73744.0,
      "end_time": 76435.0,
      "text": "What if the oil actually got where it was trying to go?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77740.0,
      "end_time": 81710.0,
      "text": "Not only would it have been burned in engines and added to global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81950.0,
      "end_time": 84456.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a place called \"Cancer Alley,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84480.0,
      "end_time": 86615.0,
      "text": "and the reason it&#39;s called \"Cancer Alley\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86639.0,
      "end_time": 89267.0,
      "text": "is because the petrochemical industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89291.0,
      "end_time": 91447.0,
      "text": "takes that oil and turns it into plastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91471.0,
      "end_time": 93651.0,
      "text": "and in the process, kills people."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94174.0,
      "end_time": 97222.0,
      "text": "It shortens the lives of the people who live there in the Gulf."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97246.0,
      "end_time": 101390.0,
      "text": "So oil and petrochemicals are not just a problem when there&#39;s a spill;"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101640.0,
      "end_time": 102773.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re a problem when there&#39;s not."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102798.0,
      "end_time": 105205.0,
      "text": "And what we don&#39;t often appreciate"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105229.0,
      "end_time": 106903.0,
      "text": "is the price that poor people pay"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106927.0,
      "end_time": 109380.0,
      "text": "for us to have these disposable products."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109453.0,
      "end_time": 111598.0,
      "text": "The other thing we often don&#39;t appreciate is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111622.0,
      "end_time": 114722.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not just at the point of production that poor people suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114746.0,
      "end_time": 116919.0,
      "text": "Poor people also suffer at the point of use."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117396.0,
      "end_time": 119481.0,
      "text": "Those of us who earn a certain income level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119505.0,
      "end_time": 121446.0,
      "text": "we have something called choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121931.0,
      "end_time": 124396.0,
      "text": "The reason why you want to work hard and have a job"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124420.0,
      "end_time": 126910.0,
      "text": "and not be poor and broke"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126115.0,
      "end_time": 128555.0,
      "text": "is so you can have choices, economic choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128952.0,
      "end_time": 133370.0,
      "text": "We actually get a chance to choose not to use products"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133610.0,
      "end_time": 135278.0,
      "text": "that have dangerous, poisonous plastic in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135302.0,
      "end_time": 137837.0,
      "text": "Other people who are poor don&#39;t have those choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137861.0,
      "end_time": 139834.0,
      "text": "So low-income people often are the ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139859.0,
      "end_time": 143843.0,
      "text": "who are buying the products that have those dangerous chemicals in them"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143867.0,
      "end_time": 145305.0,
      "text": "that their children are using."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145330.0,
      "end_time": 149154.0,
      "text": "Those are the people who wind up ingesting a disproportionate amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149178.0,
      "end_time": 151345.0,
      "text": "of this poisonous plastic in using it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151369.0,
      "end_time": 154602.0,
      "text": "And people say, \"Well, they should just buy a different product.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154626.0,
      "end_time": 157761.0,
      "text": "Well, the problem with being poor is you don&#39;t have those choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157785.0,
      "end_time": 159873.0,
      "text": "You often have to buy the cheapest products."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159897.0,
      "end_time": 162876.0,
      "text": "The cheapest products are often the most dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 162900.0,
      "end_time": 164496.0,
      "text": "And if that weren&#39;t bad enough --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164520.0,
      "end_time": 167941.0,
      "text": "if it wasn&#39;t just the production of plastic that&#39;s giving people cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167965.0,
      "end_time": 169469.0,
      "text": "in places like Cancer Alley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169493.0,
      "end_time": 173100.0,
      "text": "and shortening lives and hurting poor kids at the point of use --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173250.0,
      "end_time": 175108.0,
      "text": "at the point of disposal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175132.0,
      "end_time": 178390.0,
      "text": "once again, it&#39;s poor people who bear the burden."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178762.0,
      "end_time": 181367.0,
      "text": "Often, we think we&#39;re doing a good thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181391.0,
      "end_time": 185390.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re in your office, drinking your bottled water or whatever it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185630.0,
      "end_time": 187821.0,
      "text": "and you think to yourself, \"I&#39;m going to throw this away."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 187846.0,
      "end_time": 191376.0,
      "text": "No -- I&#39;m going to be virtuous. I&#39;m going to put it in the blue bin.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191400.0,
      "end_time": 193432.0,
      "text": "You think, \"I put mine in the blue bin.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193456.0,
      "end_time": 197190.0,
      "text": "And then you look at your colleague and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 197440.0,
      "end_time": 200158.0,
      "text": "\"Why, you cretin! You put yours in the white bin.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200520.0,
      "end_time": 202806.0,
      "text": "And we use that as a moral tickle."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202830.0,
      "end_time": 204575.0,
      "text": "We feel so good about ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 204599.0,
      "end_time": 207853.0,
      "text": "If we -- well, OK, I&#39;m just ... me."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207878.0,
      "end_time": 209577.0,
      "text": "Not you, but I feel this way often."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209602.0,
      "end_time": 211236.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214150.0,
      "text": "And so we kind of have this moral feel-good moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214580.0,
      "end_time": 217386.0,
      "text": "But if we were to be able to follow that little bottle"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 217976.0,
      "end_time": 219441.0,
      "text": "on its journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219465.0,
      "end_time": 222300.0,
      "text": "we would be shocked to discover that, all too often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222540.0,
      "end_time": 224384.0,
      "text": "that bottle is going to be put on a boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225309.0,
      "end_time": 227486.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going to go all the way across the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 228146.0,
      "end_time": 229462.0,
      "text": "at some expense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 229486.0,
      "end_time": 233500.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to wind up in a developing country, often China."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 233290.0,
      "end_time": 234617.0,
      "text": "I think in our minds, we imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 234641.0,
      "end_time": 237101.0,
      "text": "somebody&#39;s going to take the little bottle and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237125.0,
      "end_time": 240386.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, little bottle! We&#39;re so happy to see you, little bottle.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240410.0,
      "end_time": 242236.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244624.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;ve served so well.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244648.0,
      "end_time": 245671.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 245695.0,
      "end_time": 247536.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s given a little bottle massage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247560.0,
      "end_time": 249236.0,
      "text": "a little bottle medal."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251458.0,
      "text": "And they say, \"What would you like to do next?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251482.0,
      "end_time": 253830.0,
      "text": "The little bottle says, \"I just don&#39;t know ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253854.0,
      "end_time": 255180.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 255204.0,
      "end_time": 257267.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not actually what happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 258350.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259500.00000000003,
      "text": "You know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259860.0,
      "end_time": 263510.0,
      "text": "That bottle winds up getting burned."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264677.0,
      "end_time": 268299.0,
      "text": "The recycling of plastic in many developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 268323.0,
      "end_time": 271472.0,
      "text": "means the incineration of the plastic, the burning of the plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 271497.0,
      "end_time": 273923.0,
      "text": "which releases incredible toxic chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 273947.0,
      "end_time": 275780.0,
      "text": "and, once again, kills people."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 275804.0,
      "end_time": 279524.0,
      "text": "And so, poor people who are making these products"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279548.0,
      "end_time": 282310.0,
      "text": "in petrochemical centers like Cancer Alley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 282334.0,
      "end_time": 285412.0,
      "text": "poor people who are consuming these products disproportionately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 285436.0,
      "end_time": 288950.0,
      "text": "and then poor people who, even at the tail end of the recycling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 288974.0,
      "end_time": 290736.0,
      "text": "are having their lives shortened."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 290760.0,
      "end_time": 294356.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all being harmed -- greatly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 294380.0,
      "end_time": 298867.0,
      "text": "by this addiction that we have to disposability."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 299244.0,
      "end_time": 301726.0,
      "text": "Now, you think to yourself -- I know how you are --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 301750.0,
      "end_time": 305220.0,
      "text": "you say, \"That sure is terrible for those poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 306538.0,
      "end_time": 309426.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just awful. Those poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 310760.0,
      "end_time": 312207.0,
      "text": "I hope someone does something to help them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 312862.0,
      "end_time": 314588.0,
      "text": "But what we don&#39;t understand is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 316250.0,
      "end_time": 317825.0,
      "text": "here we are in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 317850.0,
      "end_time": 319981.0,
      "text": "We worked very hard to get the smog reduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 320500.0,
      "end_time": 321560.0,
      "text": "happening here in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 321584.0,
      "end_time": 322815.0,
      "text": "But guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 322839.0,
      "end_time": 326194.0,
      "text": "Because they&#39;re doing so much dirty production in Asia now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 326218.0,
      "end_time": 329826.0,
      "text": "because the environmental laws don&#39;t protect the people in Asia now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 329850.0,
      "end_time": 333892.0,
      "text": "almost all of the clean air gains and the toxic air gains"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 333916.0,
      "end_time": 335788.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve achieved here in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 335812.0,
      "end_time": 338728.0,
      "text": "have been wiped out by dirty air coming over from Asia."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 339931.0,
      "end_time": 342637.0,
      "text": "So we all are being hit. We all are being impacted."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 342661.0,
      "end_time": 345415.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just that the poor people get it first and worst."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 345439.0,
      "end_time": 348630.0,
      "text": "But the dirty production, the burning of toxins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 348654.0,
      "end_time": 350914.0,
      "text": "the lack of environmental standards in Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 350938.0,
      "end_time": 353431.0,
      "text": "is actually creating so much dirty air pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 353455.0,
      "end_time": 354871.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s coming across the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 354896.0,
      "end_time": 357100.0,
      "text": "and has erased our gains here in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 357340.0,
      "end_time": 358928.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re back where we were in the 1970s."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 358952.0,
      "end_time": 360879.0,
      "text": "And so we&#39;re on one planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 360903.0,
      "end_time": 363848.0,
      "text": "and we have to be able to get to the root of these problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 363872.0,
      "end_time": 366930.0,
      "text": "The root of this problem, in my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 366954.0,
      "end_time": 369459.0,
      "text": "is the idea of disposability itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 369998.0,
      "end_time": 373190.0,
      "text": "You see, if you understand the link"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 373430.0,
      "end_time": 376771.0,
      "text": "between what we&#39;re doing to poison and pollute the planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 376795.0,
      "end_time": 379236.0,
      "text": "and what we&#39;re doing to poor people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 383394.0,
      "text": "you arrive at a very troubling but also very helpful insight:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 384296.0,
      "end_time": 386544.0,
      "text": "In order to trash the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 386568.0,
      "end_time": 388234.0,
      "text": "you have to trash people."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 388783.0,
      "end_time": 391723.0,
      "text": "But if you create a world where you don&#39;t trash people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 391747.0,
      "end_time": 393236.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t trash the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 393560.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "So now we are at a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 396500.0,
      "end_time": 398898.0,
      "text": "where the coming together of social justice as an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 398922.0,
      "end_time": 400536.0,
      "text": "and ecology as an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 401371.0,
      "end_time": 402656.0,
      "text": "we finally can now see"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 402680.0,
      "end_time": 405245.0,
      "text": "that they are really, at the end of the day, one idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 405269.0,
      "end_time": 408156.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the idea that we don&#39;t have disposable anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 408465.0,
      "end_time": 411650.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have disposable resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 411560.0,
      "end_time": 414191.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have disposable species."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 414215.0,
      "end_time": 416770.0,
      "text": "And we don&#39;t have disposable people, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 416795.0,
      "end_time": 418817.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have a throwaway planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418841.0,
      "end_time": 421632.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t have throwaway children -- it&#39;s all precious."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 421656.0,
      "end_time": 424536.0,
      "text": "And as we all begin to come back to that basic understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 424560.0,
      "end_time": 427536.0,
      "text": "new opportunities for action begin to emerge."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 428155.0,
      "end_time": 429825.0,
      "text": "Biomimicry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 429850.0,
      "end_time": 433367.0,
      "text": "which is an emerging science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 433391.0,
      "end_time": 436536.0,
      "text": "winds up being a very important social justice idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 436996.0,
      "end_time": 439188.0,
      "text": "People who are just learning about this stuff:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 439212.0,
      "end_time": 442798.0,
      "text": "biomimicry means respecting the wisdom of all species."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 443211.0,
      "end_time": 444375.0,
      "text": "Democracy, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 444399.0,
      "end_time": 447406.0,
      "text": "means respecting the wisdom of all people -- we&#39;ll get to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 447430.0,
      "end_time": 450216.0,
      "text": "But biomimicry means respecting the wisdom of all species."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 450240.0,
      "end_time": 452750.0,
      "text": "It turns out we&#39;re a pretty clever species."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 452774.0,
      "end_time": 455853.0,
      "text": "We have this big cortex, we&#39;re pretty proud of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 455877.0,
      "end_time": 458440.0,
      "text": "But if we want to make something hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 458464.0,
      "end_time": 460978.0,
      "text": "we say, \"I know! I&#39;m going to make a hard substance."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 461200.0,
      "end_time": 464536.0,
      "text": "I know! I&#39;m going to get vacuums and furnaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 464560.0,
      "end_time": 466244.0,
      "text": "and drag stuff out of the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 466268.0,
      "end_time": 469157.0,
      "text": "and get things hot and poison and pollute ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 469181.0,
      "end_time": 471402.0,
      "text": "But I got this hard thing!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 472640.0,
      "end_time": 473214.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 473238.0,
      "end_time": 474837.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m so clever!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 474861.0,
      "end_time": 477906.0,
      "text": "And you look behind you, and there&#39;s destruction all around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 477930.0,
      "end_time": 479830.0,
      "text": "But guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 479107.0,
      "end_time": 481653.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re so clever, but you&#39;re not as clever as a clam."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 481964.0,
      "end_time": 483201.0,
      "text": "A clamshell is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 483718.0,
      "end_time": 486389.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no vacuums. There&#39;s no big furnaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 486413.0,
      "end_time": 488353.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no poison. There&#39;s no pollution."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 488377.0,
      "end_time": 493177.0,
      "text": "It turns out that other species figured out a long time ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 493201.0,
      "end_time": 495536.0,
      "text": "how to create many of the things we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 495560.0,
      "end_time": 498536.0,
      "text": "using biological processes that nature knows how to use well."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 499223.0,
      "end_time": 502898.0,
      "text": "That insight of biomimicry, of our scientists finally realizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 502922.0,
      "end_time": 505330.0,
      "text": "that we have as much to learn from other species --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 505354.0,
      "end_time": 508536.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean taking a mouse and sticking it with stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 508560.0,
      "end_time": 511869.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean looking at it from that way, abusing the little species."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 511893.0,
      "end_time": 515149.0,
      "text": "I mean actually respecting them, respecting what they&#39;ve achieved."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 515173.0,
      "end_time": 516730.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s called biomimicry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 516754.0,
      "end_time": 520627.0,
      "text": "and that opens the door to zero waste production;"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 520650.0,
      "end_time": 522535.0,
      "text": "zero pollution production;"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 522558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524536.0,
      "text": "that we could actually enjoy"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 524560.0,
      "end_time": 527180.0,
      "text": "a high quality of life, a high standard of living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 527205.0,
      "end_time": 528776.0,
      "text": "without trashing the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 528800.0,
      "end_time": 531839.0,
      "text": "Well, that idea of biomimicry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 531864.0,
      "end_time": 533752.0,
      "text": "respecting the wisdom of all species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 534226.0,
      "end_time": 538980.0,
      "text": "combined with the idea of democracy and social justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 538122.0,
      "end_time": 540717.0,
      "text": "respecting the wisdom and the worth of all people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 540741.0,
      "end_time": 542536.0,
      "text": "would give us a different society."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 542560.0,
      "end_time": 544431.0,
      "text": "We would have a different economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 544456.0,
      "end_time": 546766.0,
      "text": "We would have a green society"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 546790.0,
      "end_time": 549194.0,
      "text": "that Dr. King would be proud of."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 549219.0,
      "end_time": 550536.0,
      "text": "That should be the goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 550893.0,
      "end_time": 553861.0,
      "text": "And the way that we get there is to first of all recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 553885.0,
      "end_time": 555968.0,
      "text": "that the idea of disposability"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 556826.0,
      "end_time": 560936.0,
      "text": "not only hurts the species we&#39;ve talked about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 560960.0,
      "end_time": 563711.0,
      "text": "but it even corrupts our own society."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 563735.0,
      "end_time": 566712.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re so proud to live here in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 566736.0,
      "end_time": 568822.0,
      "text": "We just had this vote, and everybody&#39;s like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 568846.0,
      "end_time": 570584.0,
      "text": "\"Well -- not in our state!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 570608.0,
      "end_time": 572128.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 572153.0,
      "end_time": 574936.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what those other states were doing, but ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 574960.0,
      "end_time": 576702.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 576726.0,
      "end_time": 578325.0,
      "text": "Just so proud."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 579321.0,
      "end_time": 581672.0,
      "text": "And, yeah, I&#39;m proud, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 581696.0,
      "end_time": 582868.0,
      "text": "But ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 584420.0,
      "end_time": 587935.0,
      "text": "California, though we lead the world in some of the green stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 587960.0,
      "end_time": 589936.0,
      "text": "we also, unfortunately, lead the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 589960.0,
      "end_time": 591500.0,
      "text": "in some of the gulag stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 592666.0,
      "end_time": 596206.0,
      "text": "California has one of the highest incarceration rates"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 596230.0,
      "end_time": 597936.0,
      "text": "of all the 50 states."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 597960.0,
      "end_time": 600196.0,
      "text": "We have a moral challenge in this movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 601770.0,
      "end_time": 606970.0,
      "text": "We are passionate about rescuing some dead materials from the landfill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 606121.0,
      "end_time": 607937.0,
      "text": "but sometimes not as passionate"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 607961.0,
      "end_time": 610279.0,
      "text": "about rescuing living beings, living people."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 610674.0,
      "end_time": 613793.0,
      "text": "And I would say that we live in a country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 613817.0,
      "end_time": 615794.0,
      "text": "five percent of the world&#39;s population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 615818.0,
      "end_time": 617684.0,
      "text": "25 percent of the greenhouse gases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 618332.0,
      "end_time": 620567.0,
      "text": "but also 25 percent of the world&#39;s prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 621344.0,
      "end_time": 624400.0,
      "text": "One of every four people locked up anywhere in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 624280.0,
      "end_time": 626202.0,
      "text": "is locked up right here in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 626226.0,
      "end_time": 628936.0,
      "text": "So that is consistent with this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 628960.0,
      "end_time": 631596.0,
      "text": "that disposability is something we believe in."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 632176.0,
      "end_time": 633335.0,
      "text": "And yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 634500.0,
      "end_time": 639220.0,
      "text": "as a movement that has to broaden its constituency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 639460.0,
      "end_time": 640357.0,
      "text": "that has to grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 640381.0,
      "end_time": 643483.0,
      "text": "that has to reach out beyond our natural comfort zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 643507.0,
      "end_time": 646420.0,
      "text": "one of the challenges to the success of this movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 646444.0,
      "end_time": 649684.0,
      "text": "of getting rid of things like plastic and helping the economy shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 649708.0,
      "end_time": 652655.0,
      "text": "is people look at our movement with some suspicion."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 653124.0,
      "end_time": 655720.0,
      "text": "And they ask a question, and the question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 655744.0,
      "end_time": 657711.0,
      "text": "How can these people be so passionate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 658506.0,
      "end_time": 661745.0,
      "text": "A poor person, a low-income person, somebody in Cancer Alley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 661769.0,
      "end_time": 664203.0,
      "text": "somebody in Watts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 664227.0,
      "end_time": 666935.0,
      "text": "somebody in Harlem, somebody on an Indian reservation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 666960.0,
      "end_time": 669178.0,
      "text": "might say to themselves -- and rightfully so --"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 669202.0,
      "end_time": 671219.0,
      "text": "\"How can these people be so passionate"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 672108.0,
      "end_time": 673848.0,
      "text": "about making sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 673873.0,
      "end_time": 677936.0,
      "text": "that a plastic bottle has a second chance in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 677960.0,
      "end_time": 680703.0,
      "text": "or an aluminum can has a second chance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 681171.0,
      "end_time": 684737.0,
      "text": "and yet, when my child gets in trouble and goes to prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 684761.0,
      "end_time": 686569.0,
      "text": "he doesn&#39;t get a second chance?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 686594.0,
      "end_time": 689760.0,
      "text": "\"How can this movement be so passionate about saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 689100.0,
      "end_time": 691920.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t have throwaway stuff, no throwaway dead materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 691944.0,
      "end_time": 694759.0,
      "text": "and yet accept throwaway lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 694783.0,
      "end_time": 697100.0,
      "text": "and throwaway communities like Cancer Alley?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 697124.0,
      "end_time": 702145.0,
      "text": "And so, we now get a chance to be truly proud of this movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 702698.0,
      "end_time": 704385.0,
      "text": "When we take on topics like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 704409.0,
      "end_time": 709400.0,
      "text": "it gives us that extra call to reach out to other movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 709650.0,
      "end_time": 711407.0,
      "text": "and to become more inclusive and to grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 711431.0,
      "end_time": 714668.0,
      "text": "and we can finally get out of this crazy dilemma that we&#39;ve been in."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 715229.0,
      "end_time": 717340.0,
      "text": "Most of you are good, softhearted people."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 718649.0,
      "end_time": 721305.0,
      "text": "When you were younger, you cared about the whole world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 721329.0,
      "end_time": 724224.0,
      "text": "and at some point, somebody said you had to pick an issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 725980.0,
      "end_time": 727169.0,
      "text": "you had to boil your love down to an issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 727542.0,
      "end_time": 729650.0,
      "text": "\"Can&#39;t love the whole world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 729890.0,
      "end_time": 732683.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got to work on trees or you&#39;ve got to work on immigration."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 732707.0,
      "end_time": 735611.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got to shrink it down and be about one issue.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 735635.0,
      "end_time": 737795.0,
      "text": "And really, they fundamentally told you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 738579.0,
      "end_time": 740104.0,
      "text": "\"Are you going to hug a tree?"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 740713.0,
      "end_time": 742839.0,
      "text": "Or are you going to hug a child? Pick."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 742864.0,
      "end_time": 744476.0,
      "text": "Are you going to hug a tree?"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 744500.0,
      "end_time": 746569.0,
      "text": "Or are you going to hug a child? Pick.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 746593.0,
      "end_time": 749450.0,
      "text": "Well, when you start working on issues like plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 749690.0,
