      "text": "you realize the whole thing is connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 751292.0,
      "end_time": 754720.0,
      "text": "And luckily, most of us are blessed to have two arms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 754960.0,
      "end_time": 755487.0,
      "text": "we can hug both."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 755511.0,
      "end_time": 756880.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
